%F A038723 a(n) = A001653(n+1) - A001109(n). - _Antonio Alberto Olivares_, Mar 29 2008
%F A038723 Sequence satisfies -7 = f(a(n), a(n+1)) where f(u, v) = u^2 + v^2 - 6*u*v. - _Michael Somos_, Sep 28 2008
